name: PlacesToDine
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: eat nearby
des:
Now you can ask Alexa to find some nearby restaurants or places to dine in. Not just that, you can also control the number of restaurants you want Alexa to find for you.
Usage:(Example)
1) User: Alexa, Open "eat nearby"
2) Alexa: Hey..I can tell you some nearby places to dine in..... How many restaurants would you like to know?
3) User: Five
4) Alexa: Here are some places I could find....Carolina Brothers Pit Barbecue.....Mediterranean Breeze.....Urban Bar-B-Que.....Opa! mezze Grill.....Tokyo Sushi.....
